articles.title: Sunak and Modi bolster UK-India trade talks - Financial Times
articles.description: British prime minister says London and New Delhi can ‘work through’ hurdles stalling a free trade agreement
articles.content:
Rishi Sunak and Narendra Modi have injected greater impetus into UK-India trade negotiations, instructing ministers and officials to work at pace to secure a deal.
